Feature 6 – Continuous Integration with GitHub Actions

A GitHub Actions workflow was added to automatically build and test the project whenever code
is pushed to the main, bfs, or dfs branches, or when a pull request is opened against main.

The workflow file is located at .github/workflows/ci.yml and performs the following steps:

